Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:14.90,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll hold you tight and won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:17.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I've fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:20.03,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I don't want any doubts in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:23.62,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}You're special. I've met you,
