Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}This was one year ago during the school's entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}I had just arrived in Japan and didn't speak Japanese very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether I would make it or not in Japan depended on the impression I made then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I sat there, nervously waiting for my turn to introduce myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hoping I didn't say anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is... Shimada Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shimada Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we get along!{accent <3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? Did I say something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem. Shimada has been living in Germany until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't been in Japan for very long, so there'll be many things she doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll all help her get used to her new life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right, Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take your time to learn the Chinese characters{kanji}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chinese characters{Kanji}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He could've just {\i0}told{\i1} me if it was the wrong character!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so much crueler to not point it out and laugh on the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad said the Japanese are really nice people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I can't help but feel anxious about this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Came from Kannazuki Junior High School.{make this "Middle School"? Text on-screen says "junior high"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Sakamoto Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the "Man-Eater" of Kannazuki Junior High!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this kind of behavior the norm in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, Dad said Japan's one of the rare countries that maintains perfect public order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must be trying to look cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita Hideyoshi is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why she's wearing the boys' uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She probably doesn't like wearing skirts. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad said that there's nothing weird or scary in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchiya Kouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hobbies are peeping on gir— nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at eavesdrop— nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget what you just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't weird, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's gonna record the lectures with that, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should believe you, right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Nagatsuki Junior High! My name's Yoshii Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My own father tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you live in Japan before, Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you come back to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you born abroad too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A foreigner returning to Japan must've been very unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone was bombarding me with questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be very good at English, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna join a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a boyfriend in Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't understand Japanese very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so if they all talk to me at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do I tell them to slow down in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are your hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your bust size?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That girl I saw this morning said something to get rid of the boys talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should try the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cork...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cork"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cork it, you filthy pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I messed up on my very first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad told me later that I said something really horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of that, no one wanted to talk to me anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}except one boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... You're Shimada, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept this morning, so I was in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do Japanese boys wear girls' uniforms if they're in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They never teach you these things in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't block the exit while talking about your crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that, Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada is new to Japan. You shouldn't call her a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling {\i1}you{\i0} a moron, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have {\i1}I{\i0} done to be called a moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your uniform and your speech, for starters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say? Don't judge me just because of my outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's already clear that you're a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, aren't you a moron too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were ignoring that super-cute girl who was talking to you in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your fucking business, now is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your retardation has been getting on my nerves since I first saw your stupid face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line! How rude of you to call someone you just met a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to be courteous to an idiot who showed up at the entrance ceremony in a frickin' girl's uniform?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know what they were talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I did understand one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I got any more involved with those two, my normal school life would be history.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I can make it though this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was really worried if I made the right decision to come to Japan with Hazuki because of Dad's transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, in Japan, the girls' restroom is blue, and the boys' restroom is pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would've been so embarrassing if I hadn't noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are these two girls in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt! I am not a girl—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come with me, Kinoshita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thou art mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did thee drag me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What were you doing in the men's restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What art thee enraged about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am just a man, going about his business—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hark! Shimada!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still didn't understand Japan very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, it's only my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll surely learn in the coming days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, I'll be patient and try to get along—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I don't get Japan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They really {\i0}are{\i1} unique.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A week has passed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Classes have started for real now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still haven't really gotten used to Japanese,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so wrapping my head around Modern Japanese was rather difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the language in the classics read like pure gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, what's the conjugated form of {\i1}haberi{\i0} ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}hannari{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lecture is on classic conjugation, but your answer is in the Kyoto dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like how you gave me the answer to the next lesson in two days.{as in, the class on the day after tomorrow will be on Kyoto dialect, and Aki's answer would have fit then, not now}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, review what we covered today for the next class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank God it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I almost died of boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shimada, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ich gehe nach home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What a sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. "I'm going home."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I couldn't really understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just came back from abroad, so I thought you were speaking in a foreign language.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only knew a little Japanese, so I couldn't understand his fast speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really tried to make sense of it, but my mind just couldn't keep up and went {\i0}pop{\i1} like a flat tire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{gibberish}I want to go home too, but we still have homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Eh?}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:13:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{more gibberish, can't find this in the novel, so probably not TL the above line too for consistency?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it so funny that I can't speak Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think he said, "What clubs were you in when you is{sic} in junior high, Minami?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but why is he asking that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His own grammar is wrong in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... {\i1}Tunevoudrais...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't they understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, I fit into the class as badly as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't make friends because I couldn't understand Japanese,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so no one would even talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a vicious cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's because I messed up my first impression on the first day of school...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when I wrote down the wrong characters for my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure I never corrected this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some guys from{"used to go to," but this line seems really long} Agebono Junior High want to play basketball with the stakes being candy at the student shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of money for food for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to participate too. It sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did they become such good pals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no idea what he's saying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't he know I don't understand Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with the "Monamie" anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name's Minami, not Monamie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't even remember my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't act so familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tune—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\i1}Dontok tumi{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{What a shit man you are!}{this is so embarrassing. subbed already at least}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm a man. What about you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a guy, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're a man, Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't even English get through to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{What a shit man you are.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you're annoying as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve calling an angry girl a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, Shimada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were a man just because your chest is so flat—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's breaking my elbow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand Japanese, but I somehow heard him call my chest flat crystal clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{What a shit man you are!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This sucks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I had never come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only just met, so I don't really know for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think that idiot is a pretty interesting guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...diot?{TL Note: She doesn't know what the Japanese word baka means}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go look up what he was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, it means "idiot."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already know he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet he was making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll look up what he said and completely embarrass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tunevoudraispas... Tunevoudraispas... Tunevoudraispas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't find any words that fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What {\i0}did{\i1} he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it even correct Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He sure didn't get my name right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Minami, not Monamie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mon amie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}France.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tunevoudraispasdevenir monamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not German either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He mixed it up and translated it into French.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's really a complete idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The library doesn't have a German-to-French dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have to translate it to English first, and from there to German.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know the French spellings, so I have no clue whether I'm transcribing the sounds correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:20:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu ne voudrais pas{\i1} means "Wouldn't you" in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devenir{\i1} means "become".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monamie{\i1} is {\i0}mon amie{\i1}, "my friend".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you put it together,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure he looked it up just like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though it was an unknown language of a foreign country...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he has trouble with the literature of his own country...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's an idiot, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A damn idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he's such an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(500,500)}Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Good morning, Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up, Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a shit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Have I done something to offend you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...{TL Note: This is why Minami refers to herself with uchi instead of watashi}{TL Note: shit's hot.}
