Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 9.
Dialogue: 6,0:23:37.18,0:23:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it called when an organization attempts to influence the government's decisions by bribing{influencing} politicians?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "mixer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's being mixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Me, romance, and the art of negotiation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.72,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami, do you want to stay here in Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:44.77,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)}If you really want to, I'll make arrangements for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:46.98,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.23,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you come with me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:52.69,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.61,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you, Hazuki.
