Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.65,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:02.69,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.11,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.28,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,How was school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.20,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.12,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.12,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I made a ton of wonderful friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.62,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.04,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Japan really {\i1}is{\i0} a great country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.46,derpytextatbeginning,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
